This repository contains the data architecture and visualization logic behind the Executive Sales Dashboard, built to deliver high-level insights into global sales performance, operational efficiency, and explosive year-over-year (YoY) growth across multiple business dimensions.

The project enables stakeholders to quickly assess business health, identify growth drivers, and make data-driven strategic decisions.

